CustomProperties.Name: DelayOutput
CustomProperties.Tooltip: When set to true, user input is registered after half a second delay. Useful for delaying expensive operations until user completes inputting text.

CustomProperties.Name: ClearIcon
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle the visibility of the clear text icon, in order to clear all text in the text box.

CustomProperties.Name: PrimaryOrange
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to toggle the primary color.

CustomProperties.Name: onSelect
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the onSelect property of the text input.

Rules.InvariantScript: If('Search Box'.ClearIcon = true, If(TextInput3_2.Text = "", false, true), false)
